PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of MEEKA WALSH, of Winnipeg, Manitoba, as a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the National Gallery of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Judy MacDonald, whose term has expired.
